e:["$","p",null,{"className":"x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:leading-7","children":"This is the entire contract. A plugin knows about the bus and nothing else. It doesn’t hold references to other plugins. It doesn’t know what order it was loaded in (except for the guarantees described below)."}]
